  "body": "I noticed that the input's value is not updated in the DOM when implementing a controlled component. Is this normal / expected behavior?\n\n```\n<div>\n  <input\n    // Controlled Component\n    value={this.state.term}\n    onChange={(event) => this.setState({ term: event.target.value })} />\n</div>\n```\n\nHere is a link to an example on JSBin (When it first loads press 'Run with JS' button in Output section):\nhttp://jsbin.com/sodojo/1/edit?html,js,output\n",
